  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Smogshadow Hunter\" is an intense first-person shooter where you play as a hunter entering a confined warehouse shrouded in black fog to hunt down malfunctioning robots. The game offers a variety of weapons, each providing a unique shooting experience. The black fog severely limits visibility, and players must rely on sound to defeat their enemies.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person perspective for full immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A diverse weapon system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Black fog environment adds a tense hunting experience!</p></li></ul>",
